    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >大家好，我是这款游戏的作者凉鞋。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《我的玫瑰》是一款像素风精确平台跳跃游戏。男孩为救女孩出发寻找灵魂果，他能否顺利收集灵魂果呢？最终又能否拯救女孩儿呢？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246640/extras/ee756a1b7d129907f250fc845a325fcb.poster.avif?t=1743998571\" width=468 height=402 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246640/extras/ee756a1b7d129907f250fc845a325fcb.webm?t=1743998571\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246640/extras/ee756a1b7d129907f250fc845a325fcb.mp4?t=1743998571\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏中主要包含精心设计的 60+ 关卡，4 个主角能力<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246640/extras/c6e20016a418a4f12639b592df893c10.webp?t=1743998571\" width=16 height=16 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246640/extras/5441e5badf3f34231eb356d610364fda.webp?t=1743998571\" width=16 height=16 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246640/extras/4577a7835121825f5c558d2816c1b663.webp?t=1743998571\" width=16 height=16 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246640/extras/112386a916419b6468adb64f6958dcd9.webp?t=1743998571\" width=16 height=16 /></span>,2 种机关陷阱<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246640/extras/594e6194e898a538fde2140e429aa1dd.webp?t=1743998571\" width=16 height=16 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246640/extras/68bcb2cd0a90b5669c94a5628bb475b3.webp?t=1743998571\" width=16 height=16 /></span>和 1 个简简单单的故事。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246640/extras/78ecaef0093c7ca733d9a58f4e8d7e7f.poster.avif?t=1743998571\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246640/extras/78ecaef0093c7ca733d9a58f4e8d7e7f.webm?t=1743998571\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246640/extras/78ecaef0093c7ca733d9a58f4e8d7e7f.mp4?t=1743998571\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >难易结合并且变化多样的玩儿法，可以让大家从一开始就进入状态，在不断尝试中层层突破，推进游戏，获得轻松休闲和紧张刺激的双重体验！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏通关时长约 1～2 小时，除通关<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246640/extras/04df5872dfab16c07b9cfb7ac25cd036.webp?t=1743998571\" width=16 height=16 /></span>之外还设置了 3 种额外挑战<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246640/extras/a4eb68c383cd2de97240f9d3aa455088.webp?t=1743998571\" width=16 height=16 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246640/extras/97a4d94ebb62feaa7b0f0baef0140f59.webp?t=1743998571\" width=16 height=16 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246640/extras/f14fc19da71165515a2c97a7c04f6300.webp?t=1743998571\" width=16 height=16 /></span>，成就感加满！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246640/extras/3dd73eb12b4cb196842c33cc88b52e44.poster.avif?t=1743998571\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246640/extras/3dd73eb12b4cb196842c33cc88b52e44.webm?t=1743998571\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246640/extras/3dd73eb12b4cb196842c33cc88b52e44.mp4?t=1743998571\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《我的玫瑰》是作者第一款真正意义上的独立游戏。游戏设计，编程，美术，部分音乐音效都是由作者一人完成，希望你会喜欢这个作品，也希望这世间的一切都有一个美好的结局。</p>",
